FAQs

Questions? We’ve got answers.

Everything you need to know about the product and billing. Can’t find the answer you’re looking for? Please contact support@staticflow.io.

Where do I make the ads?

Our templates are created inside of Canva & Figma. Simply click the “Canva” button and you will be taken to a Canva URL. Inside of Canva you can easily customize the template, add your branding elements, write some copy & get to testing! Alternatively, you can click the "Figma" button and it will copy the templates to your clipboard.

How many ad templates are there?

Our ad library consists of 1000+ templates that you will have access to when you purchase a premium plan. We add an additional 50+ new ad templates every week so you never run out of fresh ideas and concepts.

Can I save ads for later?

Yes! Just hit the save icon next to any creative you like & head to the "Saved ads" tab!

Are they guaranteed to perform?

All of our ads are selected based on our strict performance criteria and are selected with performance in mind. However, even though these are working for other brands, it does not necessarily mean it will work for your brand. This is why we recommend testing a variety of ads and see what resonates best with your audience.

What if I want to cancel?

You can cancel your subscription anytime. You will continue to have access until the end of the billing period. For annual subscriptions this means you will have access until the end of the billing year, but your plan won't renew for another term.
